description:
November 2, 2015 / The team reports on Adnan Syed's lawyer, Cristina Gutierrez. They discuss her background, career, and unfortunate illness before her death.

Special thanks to Patrick Cortes (AKA Animalweapon) for creating original scoring music for Undisclosed. You can find more music by Patrick on Soundcloud.
